reviewText: Great Story!  My son loves the 2 movies as well (Dolphin Tale and Dolphin Tale 2)
A touching true story. Will melt your heart.  Great production.
Real live footage of the rescues of Winter and Hope, and touching and emotional examples of how Winter and Hope inspire humans.

This movie was decent but nothing like Dolphin Tale. It was actually pretty sad but I am not the type that likes to watch hurting children even if its a "Happy" story. My girlfriend is a huge Winter supporter and she didn't even like the movie.
Loved the movie so awesome thanks
It was very interesting to learn what really happened and see what great worked they do
My 13 year old youth loved it. She is a big fan of Winter so she was excited to see it.

Packaged well and arrived on time.
If you liked or loved the movie, you will enjoy this.  This is a tear jerker, especially because this shows the really people that were inspired by Winter.
I loved the live footage and the true stories of the people who inspired the movies Dolphin Tale & Dolphin Tale 2. Great movie with a lot of inspiration and efforts of the Clearwater Marine Aquarium.
Uplifting and moving.  A great family movie made better when we visited the Clearwater Marine Aquarium and actually saw Winter.  Amazing!!
Not what I expected, and a little long... but I found it very interesting and our kids that love both Dolphin Tale movies enjoyed it. For the price, it's worth it.
